			<CASNumber>CID 313</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Hydrochloric acid, also known as muriatic acid or spirits of salt, is an aqueous solution of hydrogen chloride. It is a colorless solution with a distinctive pungent smell. It is classified as a strong acid. Hydrochloric acid is the aqueous solution of hydrogen chloride gas and the main component of gastric acid, an acid produced naturally in the human stomach to help digest food. It is synthetically produced for a variety of industrial and commercial applications.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">盐酸，又称盐酸或盐精，是氯化氢的水溶液。它是一种无色溶液，具有独特的刺激性气味。它被归类为强酸。盐酸是氯化氢气体的水溶液，也是胃酸的主要成分，胃酸是人体胃部自然产生的一种酸，有助于消化食物。它是为各种工业和商业应用而合成的。</common:generalComment>
